ext.settings.angular.controlFlowPrefix:
Matches Angular's control flow keyword prefix (@).

* `@`if (showBody) { &#60;body-cmp/&#62; }

* `@`else if (showSummary) { &#60;summary-cmp/&#62; }

* `@`else { Nothing to see here }

```html

